## 1️⃣ 创建命名空间

```yaml
# k8s/namespace.yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Namespace
metadata:
  name: microservice
  labels:
    name: microservice
    environment: production
```

**执行命令：**
```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/namespace.yaml
```

